main event: USO was observed on APS-24 radar while tracking an RB-36.
interesting points: The USO was detected on the radar system of an RB-36 aircraft,The observation was confirmed by USA observers on the same radar,The identified flight was made by the 63rd Strat Recon Squadron,The altitude of the radar was approximately 14,322 feet,The report stated that photographs were not received, and there was insufficient data for evaluation.
